<emphasis bold="true" box="[271,301,976,996]" pageId="6" pageNumber="333">12.</emphasis>
New record from Córdoba: 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Selys" baseAuthorityYear="1857" box="[573,721,976,996]" class="Insecta" family="Libellulidae" genus="Erythemis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="6" pageNumber="333" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="attala">
